WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.230
First off is planning. During the planning phase, participants are selected,

00:00:04.230 --> 00:00:08.550
a meeting is scheduled, roles are assigned, the specific artifact, or

00:00:08.550 --> 00:00:13.170
part of an artifact is specified. And the materials, that is, the artifact,

00:00:13.170 --> 00:00:16.560
the review form, and any background materials, are distributed to the,

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.800
the participants. This planning should be complete about five days

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.290
before the scheduled meeting, to give time for the participants to prepare.

